data.description: This Milwood home is just waiting for you! Livingroom with wood burning fireplace., kitchen with stainless steel refrigerator,also included the  range and dishwasher. Two bedrooms and remodeled bathroom finish off the main level. Downstairs has a large storage room, the laundry area with washer and dryer, and huge open area with the mechanicals.  The large backyard is fenced in and has a new shed. There is a single stall garage. Updates in the last 2 years or less is a new roof , new windows, new central air and furnace, new water softener, new water heater, new shed and the remodeled bathroom. Make your appointment to view this home now!
